Definition: an agreement to buy or sell a specific amount of a commodity or financial instrument at a particular price on a stipulated future date
Example: the contract can be sold before the settlement date
Synonyms: derivative_instrument, an, agreement, to, buy, or, sell, a, specific, amount, of, commodity, financial, instrument, at, particular, price, on, stipulated, future, date, the, contract, can, be, sold, before, settlement
Category: noun.communication
